description.narrative: As custodian of child related SDG data, UNICEF continues to support the national statistical office (BPS) to pilot new global methods to collect data on child related SDG indicators, including the Early Child Development index and child disability. In response to the COVID-19 pandemic, UNICEF is supporting BPS to collect data on the impact of COVID-19 on children and families in Indonesia to strengthen the national capacity for monitoring the longer-term impact through national household surveys. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:15/07/2020
